@node "Features" "Features"
TrapListPrefs is an intition based preference editor for TrapList.

Features:
    o Allows you to set all the features of TrapList
    o All options can be set with simple cycle gadgets, and string
      gadgets.
    o Full locale support.
    o Both a MUI and a BGUI user interface
    o Freely redistributable @{"SHAREWARE" link "shareware" 0}.
@endnode

